Package alluxio.client.file

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileSystem
    Basic file system interface supporting metadata operations and data operations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseFileSystem
    Default implementation of the FileSystem interface.
    DelegatedUnderStoreStreamFactory
    Factory which creates input streams to a specified path in under storage.
    DirectUnderStoreStreamFactory
    Factory which creates input streams to a specified path in under storage.
    FileInStream
    A streaming API to read a file.
    FileOutStream
    Provides a streaming API to write a file.
    FileSystem.Factory
    Factory for FileSystem.
    FileSystemMasterClient
    A wrapper for the thrift client to interact with the file system master, used by alluxio clients.
    FileSystemMasterClientPool
    A fixed pool of FileSystemMasterClient instances.
    FileSystemUtils
    Collection of utility methods to handle with FileSystem related objects.
    FileSystemWorkerClient
    Client for talking to a file system worker server.
    UnderFileSystemFileInStream
    Provides a streaming API to read a file in the under file system through an Alluxio worker's data server.
    UnderFileSystemFileOutStream
    Provides a streaming API to write to a file in the under file system through an Alluxio worker's data server.
    UnderFileSystemFileOutStream.Factory
    Factory for creating an UnderFileSystemFileOutStream.
    UnknownLengthFileInStream
    A streaming API to read a file of unknown length.
    URIStatus
    Wrapper around FileInfo.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileSystemContext
    A shared context in each client JVM for common file master client functionality such as a pool of master clients.
